thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Phillip Carrero, Carrero Art.

author: Phillip Carrero, Carrero Art.
title: Phillip Carrero, Carrero Art.
text: I've used Pack and Send for a couple of years now. The couriers they use are very responsible with fast deliveries and no mishaps. Price-wise they match or better other outfits. Cheaper PayPal option. All in all I'm happy with this.
